+
+PortPulse is an **API-first metrics service** for port congestion, dwell, snapshots, trends, alerts, and HS imports (beta).  
+You get **reliable, auditable indicators** in **JSON or CSV**, with strong caching (**ETag/304**).
+
+**Base URL**: `https://api.useportpulse.com`  
+**Versioning**: stable `/v1` (breaking changes go to `/v1beta`, deprecation ≥ 90 days)
+
+### Why PortPulse?
+
+- First `200` in **≤ 5 minutes**, ~**30 minutes** to production
+- p95 latency **< 300 ms** with edge caching; **CSV ETag/304** enabled
+- Freshness target **p95 ≤ 2h**
+- Availability **99.9% SLA** (Pro)
+- Coverage target **≥ 67 ports** with 30-day replay
+
+### Authentication
+
+Send your key in `X-API-Key`.
+
+```http
+GET /v1/health
+X-API-Key: DEMO_KEY
+```
+
+### Quickstart
