+- Language snippets: **[Quickstarts](/docs/Guides/quickstarts)**
+- API clients: **[Postman](/docs/postman)** · **[Insomnia](/docs/insomnia)**
+- Full surface/parameters: **[OpenAPI](/openapi)**
+
+### CSV + ETag/304
+
+Prefer `If-None-Match` with CSV to avoid re-downloading unchanged data. Details: **[CSV & ETag](/docs/csv-etag)**.
+
+### Errors & Rate limits
+
+- Standard error body: `{code, message, request_id, hint}`
+- See **[Errors](/docs/errors)** and **[Rate limits](/docs/rate-limits)**
